OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FA German YouTuber has won a famous
OL,7,FGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,8,Fafter edging out a local man who came
OL,9,Fout of retirement to see off the
OL,10,Fpretender to his crown.
OL,12,FRecent double champion Tom Kopke, 24,
OL,13,Fpipped Guinness World Record holder
OL,14,FChris Anderson close to the finish
OL,15,Fline, after chasing an 8lb double
OL,16,FGloucester cheese down Cooper's Hill
OL,17,Fin Brockworth, before declaring: "This
OL,18,Fyear's cheese will taste the sweetest
OL,19,Fof all the cheeses I have won."
OL,26,@yD@bOU{D@_O]
