PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FBoth men risked risked broken bones
OL,7,Fand serious injury, as they joined
OL,8,Fabout two dozen daredevils to throw
OL,9,Fthemselves down a steep hill in the
OL,10,Fannual death-defying cheese-rolling
OL,11,Frace in Gloucestershire.
OL,13,FBrave competitors sprinted, tripped
OL,14,Fand tumbled down Cooper's Hill in
OL,15,FBrockworth to try to win the double
OL,16,FGloucester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
