FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FThe heavy spring rain had softened the
OL,7,Ftrack, but the recent hot weather had
OL,8,Fmade it firmer and more dangerous for
OL,9,Fthe competitors who were cheered on by
OL,10,Fthousands of spectators.
OL,12,FWith temperatures soaring during what
OL,13,Fforecasters said could become the
OL,14,Fhottest spring bank holiday on record,
OL,15,Fcompetitors and spectators alike also
OL,16,Fhad to contend with sweltering
OL,17,Fconditions and the mercury hitting
OL,18,Fnearly 30C in Gloucestershire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
