PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FThere was an extra competitive edge to
OL,7,Fthis year's races as Guinness World
OL,8,FRecord holder Chris Anderson, 38, came
OL,9,Fout of retirement after being
OL,10,Fchallenged by YouTuber and recent
OL,11,Fdouble champion Tom Kopke, 24.
OL,13,FMr Kopke, from Munich, came out on top
OL,14,Fafter pipping Mr Anderson close to the
OL,15,Ffinish line in the first men's
OL,16,Fdownhill race.
OL,18,FThe German, who retained the title he
OL,19,Fhas won the previous two years, was
OL,20,Fembraced by his rival at the bottom
OL,21,Fafter being declared the winner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,F"This was I think my best year ever
OL,7,Fand I tried to stay on my feet for as
OL,8,Flong as possible," Mr Kopke said.
OL,10,F"I don't know how it went but I gave
OL,11,Feverything. It's everyone's race and
OL,12,Fyou have just got to give your best
OL,13,Fand the best man wins.
OL,15,F"The hill was better than last year as
OL,16,Fthe hill was really dry, but this year
OL,17,Fit was the optimal conditions ` not
OL,18,Ftoo dry and a bit soft so the falls
OL,19,Fgot cushioned.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
