FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,F"I think I got a good recovery on the
OL,7,Fmiddle of the hill and then sprinted
OL,8,Fthe rest.
OL,10,F"This year's cheese will taste the
OL,11,Fsweetest of all the cheeses I have
OL,12,Fwon."
OL,14,FAsked how he prepares, he said: "Shut
OL,15,Foff your brain and go for it. The
OL,16,Fentire race I saw Chris in front of me
OL,17,Fand I had to get him."
OL,19,FMr Anderson, from Brockworth, has won
OL,20,F23 times between 2005 and 2022.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@EO]vD@aOUyD@VO]
