OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FRebel cheese rollers have been staging
OL,7,Ftheir own unofficial event after
OL,8,Fhealth and safety fears caused the
OL,9,Fofficial competition to be cancelled
OL,10,Fin 2010.
OL,12,FThe cheese is chased 200 yards down
OL,13,Fthe 1:2 gradient Cooper's Hill at
OL,14,FBrockworth.
OL,16,FAfter a year's hiatus, when police
OL,17,Fwarned against the use of a real
OL,18,Fcheese, the imitation lightweight foam
OL,19,Fcheese was replaced with the genuine
OL,20,Farticle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
