OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLong-time cheese-maker Rod Smart, who
OL,12,Fhas produced cheese for the chase for
OL,13,Fmore than 25 years, once again
OL,14,Fprovided the wheels for this year's
OL,15,Fevent.
OL,17,FFour cheeses weighing about 3kg each
OL,18,Fand three smaller ones, weighing about
OL,19,F1.5kg, are used.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
