PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779753774
OL,3,CGerman YouTuber pips local man to win
OL,4,CGloucestershire cheese-rolling contest
OL,6,FThe unusual event has been celebrated
OL,7,Ffor centuries and is thought to have
OL,8,Fits roots in a heathen festival to
OL,9,Fcelebrate the return of spring.
OL,11,FThe official event was cancelled after
OL,12,Fmore than 15,000 people turned up as
OL,13,Fspectators to watch the 2009
OL,14,Fcompetition.
OL,16,FSince then, it has been held
OL,17,Funofficially, with police keeping a
OL,18,Fwatchful eye. Roads have been closed
OL,19,Fup to two and a half miles around the
OL,20,Fslope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
